sequenceDiagram
    actor Agent as AI Agent
    participant Coord as MemoryCoordinator
    participant Mgr as MemoryManager
    participant DB as MemoryDatabase
    participant SQLite as SQLite file
    participant Kuzu as Kuzu graph DB
    participant CLI as amplihack memory tree

    Agent->>Coord: store_memory(session_id, content, type)
    Coord->>Mgr: create_entry(MemoryEntry)
    Mgr->>DB: store(entry)
    DB->>SQLite: INSERT INTO memories(...)
    SQLite-->>DB: ok
    DB-->>Mgr: stored entry
    Mgr-->>Coord: success

    Note over Agent,Kuzu: Parallel: code graph indexing

    Agent->>Coord: retrieve_memories(query)
    Coord->>Mgr: search(MemoryQuery)
    Mgr->>DB: retrieve(query)
    DB->>SQLite: SELECT ... WHERE ...
    SQLite-->>DB: rows
    DB-->>Mgr: list[MemoryEntry]
    Mgr-->>Coord: results

    Note over CLI,Kuzu: User inspects memory

    actor User
    User->>CLI: amplihack memory tree --session abc
    CLI->>DB: retrieve(session_id=abc)
    DB->>SQLite: SELECT ...
    SQLite-->>DB: rows
    DB-->>CLI: entries
    CLI-->>User: tree visualization
